---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout	title="Privacy Policy - Jitan Gupta" description="Jitan Gupta is a full-stack engineer turned an entrepreneur.">
	<section class="bg-gray-100 mx-2">
		<div class="bg-white max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 rounded-b-2xl">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2">
                <li><b>Personal Information:</b> When you subscribe to our mailing list, enroll in a course, or take a quiz, we collect your name and email address.</li>
                <li><b>Payment Information:</b> If you purchase a course, payment details are processed through third-party payment gateways (e.g., Stripe, PayPal). We do not store credit card details.</li>
                <li><b>Course & Quiz Data:</b> We track quiz responses, scores, and course progress to improve user experience and provide certifications.</li>
                <li><b>Usage Data:</b> We may collect non-personal data such as IP addresses, browser type, and website usage statistics through cookies or analytics tools.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2">
                <li>To provide access to courses, quizzes, and personalized learning experiences.</li>
                <li>To process payments securely.</li>
                <li>To send you newsletters, updates, and relevant course content.</li>
                <li>To analyze quiz results and issue certifications if applicable.</li>
                <li>To improve website functionality and user experience.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. However, we may share data with trusted third-party service providers for payment processing, website analytics, and email delivery.</p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">4. Data Security & Retention</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">We take appropriate measures to protect your information. Quiz responses and course progress may be stored for up to [Insert Retention Period] for record-keeping purposes.</p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">5. Your Rights</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2">
                <li>You can opt out of our mailing list at any time.</li>
                <li>You can request deletion of your quiz responses, course data, and personal details.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">We may update this policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">7. Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">If you have any questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:hi@jitangupta.com" class="underline">hi@jitangupta.com</a>.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
